            <title>0.3.0</title>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <ul>
                  <li><b>Auto-update</b>: from this version on, ValueGuard updates itself (this is the first build with the updater).</li>
                  <li>One-click install: click <b>Install in ValueGuard</b> on the config directory and a policy downloads, verifies, and appears in the <b>Configs</b> settings tab — no terminal.</li>
                  <li>vgconfig:// URL scheme + trust-confirmation sheet (author key fingerprint, registry origin, categories, offline-verified badge).</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
